{"tid":665731,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"［改詞］《浮城》改 草東沒有派對 -《山海》","createTime":"2018-05-15T08:15:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-06T02:18:02.000Z","uid":40429,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e7880479081f3442102cc8d82419c76afec3a2bf","tid":665731,"uid":40429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T08:15:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/j2311FZWoFQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fj2311FZWoFQ&d=BRltTxiy%2FjBf63PtM8VK2C7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=dad0cccd\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/j2311FZWoFQ</a><br />\n<br />\n《浮城》<br />\n<br />\n原曲：草東沒有派對 -《山海》<br />\n改詞：善莫善於水<br />\n<br />\n無救藥<br />\n犧牲就無意義<br />\n<br />\n世界大 <br />\n怎麼遠走也可以<br />\n<br />\n無救藥<br />\n事已至此<br />\n<br />\n需求<br />\n得到一時<br />\n亦願意<br />\n<br />\n不見怪 不見怪<br />\n生存不易<br />\n太多人根本不想作主<br />\n<br />\n不見怪 不見怪<br />\n生存不易<br />\n太多人根本不是長駐<br />\n<br />\n無救藥<br />\n即使眾人皆知<br />\n<br />\n誰想與此處同歸於<br />\n<br />\n誰甘願<br />\n以沫相濡<br />\n<br />\n誰不過意氣一時<br />\n<br />\n不見怪 不見怪<br />\n生存不易<br />\n太多人根本不想作主<br />\n<br />\n不見怪 不見怪<br />\n生存不易<br />\n太多人根本不是長駐"},{"pid":"dccce0e216bc4f55ef57fa20aef9b6adc16b4793","tid":665731,"uid":4610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T08:59:27.000Z","msg":"草東<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9406e3a507e43dccec2a70e42d21fea006c373e3","tid":665731,"uid":40429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dccce0e216bc4f55ef57fa20aef9b6adc16b4793","tid":665731,"uid":4610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T08:59:27.000Z","msg":"草東<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T09:30:10.000Z","msg":"幾驚冇人識草東<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"244efcf3bba8405717f3e1471b